		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a Famicom game on a HVC-SNROM cart that I wish to reproduce in case it ever goes bad.  Are there any wiring diagrams for famicom games anywhere?  I noticed there are NES Wiring Diagrams on this site (eprom conversions on nesdev.com part) but I do not see any famicom anywhere.   Could someone help me out and point me in the right direction?  Or if you know the wiring by chance lol.  Thanks!

		

		</td>
