		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This is from Nestopia:
<br />
<br />CRC:         0xE149E0B2
<br />System:      NTSC
<br />Board/Chips: SxROM
<br />Mapper:      1
<br />PRG-ROM:     32k, CRC: 0xAF8F7059
<br />CHR-ROM:     64k, CRC: 0x031F9622
<br />W-RAM:       8k
<br />Mirroring:   Vertical

		

		</td>
	</tr>
